             was indicted for <rs id="t18320705-105-off572" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320705-105-off572" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320705-105-off572" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18320705-105-cd573" type="crimeDate">26th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320705-105-off572 t18320705-105-cd573"></join>, 1 watch, value 4l.; 1 seal, value 10s.; 2 watch-keys, value 4s., and 1 ribbon, value 1s.
            </rs>, the goods of the <rs id="t18320705-105-viclabel574" type="occupation">Rev</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320705-105-victim952 t18320705-105-viclabel574"></join>. 
               
